// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2026-2470 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: 361a7894-6491-519f-a3e1-ce39fd008495

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*oraclelinux:5*" or process.executable like~ "*oraclelinux:6*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:12.04*")
